import {Link} from 'react-router-dom';
import {Stack,Spacer,Flex,Button,Image,Box,Modal,Text,
    ModalOverlay,
    ModalContent,
    ModalHeader,
    ModalFooter,
    ModalBody,
    ModalCloseButton,
} from '@chakra-ui/react';
import { useDisclosure } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const link = [
    {
        to:"/",
        title:"Home"
    },
    {
        to:"/Meal-Deals",
        title:"Meal Deals"
    },
    {
        to:"/KindMoments",
        title:"KindMoments"
    },
    {
        to:"/Hot-Picks",
        title:"Hot Picks"
    },
    {
        to:"/Recipes",
        title:"Recipes"
    },
    {
        to:"/Directory",
        title:"Directory"
    },
    {
        to:"/Articles",
        title:"Articles"
    },
    {
        to:"/Help",
        title:"Help"
    }
]
function Navbar(){
    const { isOpen, onOpen, onClose } = useDisclosure();
    return(
        <Stack>
            <Flex border="1px solid red" height="90px" paddingLeft="30px" paddingRight="30px">
                <Box pl='5'>
                    <Link to='/'>
                        <Image src="https://www.kindmeal.my/images/logo-kindmeal.png"/>
                    </Link>
                </Box>
                <Spacer/>
                <Flex p='5' gap='5'>
                    <Box>
                        <Link to='/'>
                            <Image width="40px" height="40px" src="https://www.kindmeal.my/images/follow_blog_grey.png"/>
                        </Link>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Link to='/'>
                            <Image width="40px" height="40px" src="https://www.kindmeal.my/images/follow_facebook_grey.png"/>
                        </Link>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Link to='/'>
                            <Image width="40px" height="40px" src="https://www.kindmeal.my/images/follow_twitter_grey.png"/>
                        </Link>
                    </Box>
                </Flex>
                <Spacer/>
                <Flex mr='5' p='5'>
                    <Box p='3' mt='1' fontSize="12px" color="#444444">Login </Box>
                    <Box pt='3'>
                        <Button p='2' width="80px" height="26px" bgColor="#35619f" color="white" fontWeight="bold" fontSize="13px">Facebook</Button>  
                        <Button p='2' width="80px" height="26px" bgColor="#666666" color="white" fontWeight="bold" fontSize="13px">Email</Button>
                    </Box>
                    <Box m='3' 
                    borderLeft="1px solid grey" 
                    pl='2' pt='1' 
                    fontSize="12px" 
                    color="#444444" 
                    cursor='pointer' 
                    onClick={onOpen}
                    >
                        Signup
                    </Box>
                    <Modal isOpen={isOpen} onClose={onClose}>
                        <ModalOverlay />
                        <ModalContent height="620px" >
                            <ModalHeader paddingLeft="35px">
                                <Image src="https://www.kindmeal.my/images/logo-kindmeal.png"/>
                            </ModalHeader>
                            <ModalBody width='550px' color="#666666" fontFamily="Arial">
                                <center>
                                    <Box>
                                        <Text fontSize='1.2rem' fontWeight="bold">Join KindMeal For FREE Now</Text>
                                        <Text fontSize='0.9rem'>Please select the type of membership to proceed</Text>
                                    </Box>
                                    <Flex mt='5' p='5' border="1px solid lightgrey" borderRadius='10'>
                                        <Image src="https://www.kindmeal.my/images/join_normal.png"/>
                                        <Box pl='1'>
                                            <Text textAlign="left" fontSize='1rem' fontWeight="bold">Food Lover</Text>
                                            <Text textAlign="justify">
                                            Join FREE to enjoy yummy deals, share reviews & meet our community of compassionate food lovers.
                                            </Text>
                                        </Box>
                                    </Flex>
                                </center>
                            </ModalBody>

                            {/* <ModalFooter>
                                <Button colorScheme='blue' mr={3} onClick={onClose}>
                                Close
                                </Button>
                                <Button variant='ghost'>Secondary Action</Button>
                            </ModalFooter> */}
                        </ModalContent>
                    </Modal>
                </Flex>
            </Flex>
            <Box></Box>
        </Stack>
    )
}

export default Navbar;
